    (RelationalQueryContext)queryContext, 
    RelationalCommandCache.SelectExpression(
        Projection Mapping:
        SELECT t.Id, t.Position, t.Reminded, t.ReminderDate, t.Title, i.Id, i.Description, i.IsCompleted, i.Position, i.ToDoListId
        FROM Projection Mapping:
        (
            SELECT TOP(2) l.Id, l.Position, l.Reminded, l.ReminderDate, l.Title
            FROM Lists AS l
            WHERE l.Id == @__toDoListId_0
        ) AS t
        LEFT JOIN Items AS i ON t.Id == i.ToDoListId
        ORDER BY t.Id ASC, i.Id ASC),

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Position], [t].[Reminded], [t].[ReminderDate], [t].[Title], [i].[Id], [i].[Description], [i].[IsCompleted], [i].[Position], [i].[ToDoListId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [l].[Id], [l].[Position], [l].[Reminded], [l].[ReminderDate], [l].[Title]
    FROM [Lists] AS [l]
    WHERE [l].[Id] = @__toDoListId_0
) AS [t]
